videos.description: After the opening tip, Khris Middleton lobs it up to Giannis Antetokounmpo, who finishes with a one-handed dunk over Kevin Durant.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis electrifies with early poster dunk on Durant) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis electrifies with early poster dunk on Durant

videos.description: Kyrie Irving's shot attempt is off the mark, but Blake Griffin grabs the rebound and drops in an and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Griffin gathers Kyrie's miss for and-1) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin gathers Kyrie's miss for and-1

videos.description: DeAndre Jordan tries to throw down a dunk, but Giannis Antetokounmpo rises up to stuff the attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis denies Jordan's dunk attempt) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis denies Jordan's dunk attempt

videos.description: Kevin Durant drives in for the short floater and then sinks a 3-pointer on the next possession.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant drops in back-to-back buckets) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant drops in back-to-back buckets

videos.description: Kyrie Irving drives toward the bucket and drops in an off-balanced shot while drawing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (How does Kyrie get this and-1 to go?) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: How does Kyrie get this and-1 to go?

videos.description: DeAndre Jordan leaves Giannis Antetokounmpo wide open behind the line and he steps up and knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis shows off the range, drains 3) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis shows off the range, drains 3

videos.description: Vintage Kevin Durant crosses over PJ Tucker a couple times then splashes the mid-range jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD puts the moves on Tucker, cans jumper) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD puts the moves on Tucker, cans jumper

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo gets out in transition and goes full extension for the two-handed dunk to get to 40 points on the day.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis gets to 40 as he soars to rim for dunk) 2021/05/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis gets to 40 as he soars to rim for dunk

videos.description: Blake Griffin follows the Kevin Durant miss with a huge one-handed dunk on multiple defenders.

videos.headline: Griffin rises up for monster putback dunk

videos.description: Kevin Durant gets a good look but comes up short on the 3, giving Milwaukee the win.
